[SN]TITLE[SN]
Car driver sought after bus crashes through Wrexham railings

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The driver of a car which left the scene of a bus crash in Wrexham is being sought by police.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
A man and a girl were taken to hospital following the crash, at about 16:40 BST on Monday, 21 September at Regent Street.
North Wales Police have appealed for information about the driver of the car, a black Ford Ka, who fled the scene following the crash.
He was described as white and stocky with very short dark hair.
